LeakMonitor
LeakMonitor is a simple MVP web service that allows users to check if their email address has appeared in known data breaches using the Have I Been Pwned (HIBP) API.
It also extracts and displays the domain part of the email for potential future domain-level monitoring.

ğŸš€ Features
Check if an email has appeared in known breaches.

Display a list of breaches with names and dates (if found).

Extract and display the domain from the email.

Frontend validation of email format.

Loading spinner during checks.

âš™ Tech Stack
Node.js + Express

Axios (API requests)

Vanilla JS + HTML + CSS

dotenv (secure API key management)

